Template: opmuse/library_path
Type: string
Default: /var/cache/opmuse/music
Description: Where will you store your music and/or where do you have your music today?

Template: opmuse/library_path_perms
Type: boolean
Description: Should we automatically fix the permissions of the specified path?
 For upload, cover download and other features to work opmuse needs write
 permission to the library path. Should we automatically fix this now?

Template: opmuse/socket_host
Type: string
Default: 0.0.0.0
Description: On which address should opmuse run?

Template: opmuse/socket_port
Type: string
Default: 8080
Description: On which port should opmuse run?

Template: opmuse/user_name
Type: string
Default: admin
Description: You need to add a default user, what should its login be?

Template: opmuse/user_mail
Type: string
Default: user@example.com
Description: Provide a mail address for the user.

Template: opmuse/user_pass
Type: password
Description: Provide a password for the user.
